LALA - Licensing Avoids Legal Anxiety 

This service helps you make sure that your open source project is well licensed.
  * Avoid legal hassel
  * Enable other people to use your project with confidence

In order to use this service you will need:

  * A github account

For new projects LALA will help you:

  1. Pick a license
  2. Create a new repository
  3. Automatically maintain license declarations on the repository

For exsiting projects LALA will help you:

  1. Identify existing license declarations
  2. Pick a new license or validate an existing one
  3. Automatically maintain license declarations on the repository
